		<div class="comment_text"><p>The problem is that at this point we are so deeply entrenched in CF/Ajax, I can't even imagine us even thinking about making any technology changes.  And, again, if you have a CF/Ajax/YUI platform, what don't you have that Flex brings to the table?</p><p>That is the real issue that I can't get my head around.  WHY use Flex?  i mentioned this before, and Ray thought I was asking, 'Why RIAs', but this isn't the case.  I GET the RIA concept, and we actually use it in almost all of our apps.  I just don't understand what Flex has to offer that we aren't already getting - other than wrapping it up into one nice little package (but then, at least at our last look, you get the overhead cost that comes with it).</p></div>
