		</div>
		<div class="comment_text"><p>I am not in love with Flex 2, perhaps it was the disorganized presentation at CFUnited that first turned me off. I too do not see the need to go to a Flex engine when AJAX seems to do the trick. But as the Flex product matures and no doubt becomes more accessible for CF developers, I will take another look.</p></div>
